{"tid":710314,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple Music 免費試用一個月！","createTime":"2018-06-20T15:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T02:23:16.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb5361036de2d7781064de6a60dcfc81dd00ac2","tid":710314,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:47:22.000Z","msg":"Apple Music 又有免費兌換碼可以拿了！為了迎接本周六音樂盛事金曲獎，身為 Apple Music 台灣區代言人及這屆金曲獎入圍歌手的「JJ 林俊傑」特別準備了 Apple Music 的一個月訂閱兌換碼要送給大家，不只台灣的使用者可以兌換，香港的使用者也有專屬的兌換網頁，如果錯過了上次「莫文蔚出道 25 週年紀念 Apple Music 一個月免費兌換」的朋友，這次可就要把握機會了，兌換活動只到今年的 7 月 15 日。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cf-amod9fa3ka.zi.org.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/1529472543-9ea157e6ee9d262f2ebf88f4a2fe07ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcf-amod9fa3ka.zi.org.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F1529472543-9ea157e6ee9d262f2ebf88f4a2fe07ae.png&h=78141abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://applealmond.com/posts/34224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplealmond.com%2Fposts%2F34224&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYouv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0513db11\" target=\"_blank\">https://applealmond.com/posts/34224</a></div>"},{"pid":"ae0e1e88b0fb58ad6b006de68e45d17064c7a4d3","tid":710314,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>如何兌換林俊傑 Apple Music 兌換碼？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先，先進入這次贈送的活動網頁（<a href=\"https://applemusic.co/zh-cn/code/5b19f56321d9c53cb3464ea2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplemusic.co%2Fzh-cn%2Fcode%2F5b19f56321d9c53cb3464ea2&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYouv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=217f2de6\" target=\"_blank\">https://applemusic.co/zh-cn/code/5b19f56321d9c53cb3464ea2</a>），接著點選畫面上的「兌換」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cf-amod9fa3ka.zi.org.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/1529472773-b18f761044da28304e84f43c65fd6592-473x1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcf-amod9fa3ka.zi.org.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F1529472773-b18f761044da28304e84f43c65fd6592-473x1024.png&h=b79ded1f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n點擊兌換後會自動從網頁轉跳到 iTunes Store 的兌換頁面並自動輸入代碼，這時候我們只要點下右上角的「兌換」就可以獲得 Apple Music 一個月免費聽了。<br />\n<br />\n附註：如果沒有自動跳轉，應該會被導到一個寫著「兌換」兩字的網頁，這時只要再點一下「兌換」即可。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cf-amod9fa3ka.zi.org.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/1529473471-fa937d3cc6407284f0f304c7226e979d-768x832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcf-amod9fa3ka.zi.org.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F1529473471-fa937d3cc6407284f0f304c7226e979d-768x832.jpg&h=728df33d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"404b698d47407785586db9df43cf70e96d3dbbc7","tid":710314,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>本次 Apple Music 免費一個月兌換資格</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n這次的 Apple Music 的兌換僅有「個人訂閱計劃」的使用者可以兌換，這也代表著已經在使用 Apple Music 學生方案及家庭計劃的使用者將無法使用。如果你是還未使用過 Apple Music 的使用者，最多可以兌換到 4 個月的 Apple Music 免費使用（含試用），如果你已經是 Apple Music 的會員了，Apple Music 就會變成一個月免費，訂閱將會順延一個月。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">免費使用結束後，該如何取消訂閱？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n免費會員過期後將會自動續訂，所以原先沒有訂閱的使用者記得要去將自動定月取消，否則將會自動扣款續約。關於如何取消訂閱可以參考「取消訂閱教學」此篇教學，也可以直接至「設定」&gt;「Apple ID」&gt;「iTunes 與 App Store」&gt;「Apple ID」&gt;「檢視 Apple ID」&gt;「訂閱項目」，將 Apple Music 的訂閱取消。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>活動期限只到 7 月 15 日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大家務必把握時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</strong></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"8a9568bcef98a99d52114b361db02e77c8139ad5","tid":710314,"uid":164092,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"本身唔係有三個月免費咩？"},{"pid":"afa529c3e354a145b568bc5307546d0dc0a2f32d","tid":710314,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a9568bcef98a99d52114b361db02e77c8139ad5","tid":710314,"uid":164092,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"本身唔係有三個月免費咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:02:06.000Z","msg":"如果你是還未使用過 Apple Music 的使用者，最多可以兌換到 4 個月的 Apple Music 免費使用（含試用）"},{"pid":"5dd6d4f96a693c690d1fc662aba69bcf27a0604a","tid":710314,"uid":177447,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:09:00.000Z","msg":"7JT34RWK7KE3<br />\n<br />\n比個code大家，因為學生plan redeem唔到"},{"pid":"fe7830831c4a4a37e676c8f6f7b9aa7b57b909a1","tid":710314,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5dd6d4f96a693c690d1fc662aba69bcf27a0604a","tid":710314,"uid":177447,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:09:00.000Z","msg":"7JT34RWK7KE3<br />\n<br />\n比個code大家，因為學生plan redeem唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"做咩唔加密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a77ae369fc0f9eb2b4f0e2c82dae265c861a97c","tid":710314,"uid":177447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe7830831c4a4a37e676c8f6f7b9aa7b57b909a1","tid":710314,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5dd6d4f96a693c690d1fc662aba69bcf27a0604a","tid":710314,"uid":177447,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:09:00.000Z","msg":"7JT34RWK7KE3<br />\n<br />\n比個code大家，因為學生plan redeem唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"做咩唔加密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb112f0476af6239a99